{"tid":2280460,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"食環署宣布明年年宵市場只設濕貨攤位 不設乾貨及快餐攤位","createTime":"2020-11-10T13:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T23:04:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"26b13614a4f32b8f80bd1d630039905987e45ed5","tid":2280460,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"2021年農曆年宵市場攤位將於下周二開始公開競投。<br />\n<br />\n年宵市場由明年2月6日至2月12日，一連7天在15個地點舉行，共設有1021個濕貨攤位，集中銷售年花，場內不設乾貨及快餐攤位，為連續兩年不設乾貨攤位。年宵市場攤位競投底價凍結於去年水平，即2019年競投底價的一半，攤位底價由320元至5440元。<br />\n<br />\n食環署表示，因應疫情及紓緩年宵市場人多擠迫的情況，有必要調整年宵市場的規模。由於脫下口罩進食會增加病毒傳播的風險，因此不設快餐攤位，署方同時會擴闊公共通道，以減少密集的近距離接觸。<br />\n<br />\n入場人士進場前亦須量度體溫和時刻佩戴口罩、檔主須在其攤位提供消毒搓手液供顧客使用，並須提供其工作人員聯絡清單，以備出現確診個案時作醫學追蹤等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559314-20201110.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559314-20201110.htm&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=63602a1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559314-20201110.htm&h=6f697b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559314-20201110.htm</a>"},{"pid":"93572b68971aa623f1adea96407fd65a229aefad","tid":2280460,"uid":305767,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />開咩呀！都無生意架啦！"},{"pid":"94d727bd2c6884856858e733cb26238f102f0206","tid":2280460,"uid":134744,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"驚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎以後都唔會再有乾貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5025f8c86c60a291464be7135809eea54ff50c","tid":2280460,"uid":161726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"又冇人行了<img src=\"/assets/faces/do